parameters:
Child: "Hey, grandpa. The other day, when I went
for a walk with Gau, we got some meat from Patty-
san!"

Child: "And then, Gau was so happy eating the
meat!"

Elderly Man: "That's good to hear. Did you
remember to say thank you?"
Elderly Man: "Good, good, that's very good."

Elderly Man: "However, while meat is fine, there
are things you mustn't feed a dog, so be careful."

Ruth: "(...Not much of a conversation going on
here.)"

Ruth: "(But it's just a brat and an old man... I
can probably handle this...)"
Miu: "I'm home~ Got lots of milk today..."

Ruth: "(But it's just a brat and an old man... I
can probably handle this...)"
